W. Edwards Deming

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"William Deming" redirects here. For the Connecticut politician, see William Deming (politician).


W. Edwards Deming


Born
(1900-10-14)October 14, 1900
Sioux City, Iowa


Died
December 20, 1993(1993-12-20) (aged 93)
Washington, D.C.


Fields
Statistician


